scheduler.edit
Class Edit

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      mvp.Model
          scheduler.edit.Edit
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Edit
extends mvp.Model

Class Edit is the model class for the scheduler Tool edit handling. It contains methods for all of the operations defined on the Edit menu, which constitute the functional command group for basic editing.

Author:
Aaron Rivera

Method Detail

undo

public void undo()
Undo the most recent scheduling operation. Only one level of undo/redo is specified here. Successive invocations of undo toggle between the current and previous states of the scheduler. Note that the scheduler editing operations support undo by saving a snapshot of the input scheduler in the previous_state component of the workspace.
